data.description: Nestled just 15 minutes from downtown Houston, this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick home is a perfect blend of comfort and convenience! Inside there's a great sized kitchen with granite countertops, mahogany-colored cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast room. Adjacent to this you'll find a open plan living room boasting a beautiful fireplace. The tiled floors and an abundance of natural light, throughout, create a warm and inviting atmosphere. The master suite features an ensuite for a personal retreat. Each secondary bedroom is thoughtfully positioned for privacy, ensuring harmonious living. This home's roof, HVAC, and water heater are only 4-6 years old, coupled with the fenced backyard they ensure peace of mind. The neighborhood even has a fairy library stand, free for neighbors to add or take as needed! Enjoy great area amenities and easy access to vibrant downtown and the George Bush Intercontinental Airport. Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough.
